(32, 8, 2, 11, 16, 'FRAME_S | Office', 'frame_s-|-office', 'OffWrk8712', '5', 'Office,FURNITURE', NULL, NULL, '74000', NULL, 'Collection: Frame_s\r\nType: Office workstation\r\nManufacture year: 2016\r\nDesigner: Christian Horner', '<p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">FRAME_S</span><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;is an intelligent system&nbsp;made of frames and storage elements that can be&nbsp;merged with Bene workplace desks (T-Workstation, T-Lift Desk, Lift Desk Pure) to&nbsp;form well-organised workstations.&lrm; In addition to having&nbsp;structural functions, the frame is also a formative and striking design.&lrm;&nbsp;In an open&nbsp;space,</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;FRAME_S</span><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;serves to structure the room and at the same time the hybrid system provides a functional&nbsp;frame for wall-oriented&nbsp;workplaces with a high&nbsp;level of privacy and personal&nbsp;organisation.&lrm;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">FRAME_S</span><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;also create intermediate spaces offering well-shielded zones for teams of 3 to 6.&lrm;</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, 