(38, 8, 2, 9, 16, '36E8 MARBLE XGLASS', '36e8-marble-xglass', '36e8', '1', 'Kitchen Furniture', NULL, NULL, '1500000', NULL, '36E8 MARBLE XGLASS | Kitchen with island By Lago\r\nCollection: 36e8\r\nType: Kitchen with island\r\nManufacture year: 2019\r\nDesigner: Daniele Lago', '<p><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Work top and 36e8 base unit fronts in Statuario matt XGlass.&lrm; Breakfast bar in Wildwood naturale.&lrm; N.&lrm;O.&lrm;W.&lrm; column fronts in grafite polished glass.&lrm;</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Blocks of marble, made light by being suspended, fit into elegant, sophisticated kitchens.&lrm; Marble XGlass, thanks to the digital transfer of precious marble onto glass, unites the qualities of resistance to acidic substances and ease of cleaning of glass with the emotions of natural materials.&lrm; All with an eye to sustainability, by respecting and safeguarding natural resources.&lrm; Slim lines make the shapes refined, and the captivating continuity of the graining on the different sides emphasises their uniqueness.&lrm; The option to choose a polished or matt finish lets you interpret its character depending on the interior.&lrm;</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">The world of LAGO sideboard storage has expanded to include new modular 36e8 Glass modules that integrate both the painted and Wildwood 36e8 storage.&lrm; They are stand-alone pieces that integrate with the other elements without needing to be mounted on the wall, adding lightness and deep reflections to the space.&lrm;</span></p>', 'upload/product/thumbnail/1756473461943829.png', 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, '2023-01-30 13:33:48', NULL),
