(40, 7, 2, 6, 17, 'NIELS | Swivel easy chair', 'niels-|-swivel-easy-chair', 'Sicis', '21', 'Chair', NULL, NULL, '18000', '15500', NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Niels is a comfortable reading armchair with a moulded structure that reinterprets the past in a modern key.&lrm; Its versatility, made possible by the numerous fabrics and colours available, allows original combinations to be configured to suit different contexts, from private to public spaces.&lrm;</span></p>', 'upload/product/thumbnail/1756474014753025.png', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, '2023-01-30 13:42:35', NULL),
(41, 8, 2, 6, 19, 'JASPER By Meridiani', 'jasper-by-meridiani', 'JAS54', '23', 'Chair', NULL, NULL, '220000', '210000', 'Type: Wooden secretary desk with drawers\r\nManufacture year: 2022\r\nDesigner: Andrea Parisio', '<p><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Perfect for creating your own workstation in the living room or in the office, the Jasper desk allows you to furnish a space and do it with style, thanks to its aesthetic identity.&lrm; The multiplicity of finishes is the essence of this project, capable of combining functionality and elegance.&lrm; It is available in glossy or matt lacquer or oak, also in different combinations of top, base and drawers.&lrm;</span></p>', 'upload/product/thumbnail/1756474275861008.png', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, '2023-01-30 13:46:44', NULL),
(42, 8, 2, 5, 16, 'Fabric sofa with removable cover', 'fabric-sofa-with-removable-cover', 'SAIA 10/12', '5', 'Sofa', NULL, NULL, '872848', '870000', NULL, '<p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Saia</span><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;is a sofa defined by soft, balanced lines, designed by David Lopez Quincoces.&lrm; This sofa born from a classic ideal reinterpreted in a contemporary key.&lrm; The name Saia, meaning \"skirt\" in Portuguese, illustrates its distinctive feature: a removable cover that falls light and elegant to the ground and adheres to the structure of the sofa, emphasized and designed by a discreet piping, tone on tone or in contrast, that defines the shape.&lrm; An elegant sofa, versatile and suitable for defining different environments one from the other, Saia recalls the elegance and sweetness of a female figure: the armrests with their slight downward curvature invite you to sit comfortably to be embraced and enveloped by maximum comfort.&lrm;</span></p>', 'upload/product/thumbnail/1756474886469063.png', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2023-01-30 13:56:26', NULL),
(43, 8, 2, 1, 17, 'Sectional wall-mounted storage wall in Kera', 'sectional-wall-mounted-storage-wall-in-kera', 'Str38219', '3', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1550000', NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Wallover&reg; Composition 6&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">is a TV partition in Kera Invisible White.&lrm; Cornice is a module of the Wallover&reg; System designed to transform a TV, even a large one, into a picture.&lrm; Cables are housed in the rear technical space, so they can be managed invisibly without the need to move electrical sockets.&lrm; The Picture Frame is combined with two Bookcases that break up the rhythm of the composition and two closed elements with flap doors, called Bases.&lrm;</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">The luminous panel on the back of the TV and the LEDs embedded in the 1 cm thick shelves of the bookcases enhance the Easy Kera Invisible White backs, diffusing a soft atmospheric light.&lrm; The result is an original and lively interplay that adds charm to the controlled asymmetries and deconstructs the traditional \'TV stand\' solution.&lrm;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">FINISHES</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: #ffffff